            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3ELeviticus%204%3A1-5%3A19%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_4_1%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3ELeviticus%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EProcedures%20for%20the%20Sin%20Offering%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20said%20to%20Moses%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_4_2%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BGive%20the%20following%20instructions%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Israel.%20This%20is%20how%20you%20are%20to%20deal%20with%20those%20who%20sin%20unintentionally%20by%20doing%20anything%20that%20violates%20one%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20commands.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_4_3%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BIf%20the%20high%20priest%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E4%3A3%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20anointed%20priest%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20in%204%3A5%2C%2016.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20sins%2C%20bringing%20guilt%20upon%20the%20entire%20community%2C%20he%20must%20give%20a%20sin%20offering%20for%20the%20sin%20he%20has%20committed.%20He%20must%20present%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20a%20young%20bull%20with%20no%20defects.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_4_4%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20must%20bring%20the%20bull%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20at%20the%20entrance%20of%20the%20Tabernacle%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E4%3A4%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3ETent%20of%20Meeting%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20in%204%3A5%2C%207%2C%2014%2C%2016%2C%2018.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20lay%20his%20hand%20on%20the%20bull%26%23x2019%3Bs%20head%2C%20and%20slaughter%20it%20before%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_4_5%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20high%20priest%20will%20then%20take%20some%20of%20the%20bull%26%23x2019%3Bs%20blood%20into%20the%20Tabernacle%2C%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_4_6%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3Edip%20his%20finger%20in%20the%20blood%2C%20and%20sprinkle%20it%20seven%20times%20before%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20in%20front%20of%20the%20inner%20curtain%20of%20the%20sanctuary.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_4_7%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20priest%20will%20then%20put%20some%20of%20the%20blood%20on%20the%20horns%20of%20the%20altar%20for%20fragrant%20incense%20that%20stands%20in%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20presence%20inside%20the%20Tabernacle.%20He%20will%20pour%20out%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20bull%26%23x2019%3Bs%20blood%20at%20the%20base%20of%20the%20altar%20for%20burnt%20offerings%20at%20the%20entrance%20of%20the%20Tabernacle.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_4_8%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20priest%20must%20remove%20all%20the%20fat%20of%20the%20bull%20to%20be%20offered%20as%20a%20sin%20offering.%20This%20includes%20all%20the%20fat%20around%20the%20internal%20organs%2C%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_4_9%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3Ethe%20two%20kidneys%20and%20the%20fat%20around%20them%20near%20the%20loins%2C%20and%20the%20long%20lobe%20of%20the%20liver.%20He%20must%20remove%20these%20along%20with%20the%20kidneys%2C%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_4_10%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3Ejust%20as%20he%20does%20with%20cattle%20offered%20as%20a%20peace%20offering%2C%20and%20burn%20them%20on%20the%20altar%20of%20burnt%20offerings.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_4_11%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20he%20must%20take%20whatever%20is%20left%20of%20the%20bull%26%23x2014%3Bits%20hide%2C%20meat%2C%20head%2C%20legs%2C%20internal%20organs%2C%20and%20dung%26%23x2014%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_4_12%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3Eand%20carry%20it%20away%20to%20a%20place%20outside%20the%20camp%20that%20is%20ceremonially%20clean%2C%20the%20place%20where%20the%20ashes%20are%20dumped.%20There%2C%20on%20the%20ash%20heap%2C%20he%20will%20burn%20it%20on%20a%20wood%20fire.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_4_13%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BIf%20the%20entire%20Israelite%20community%20sins%20by%20violating%20one%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20commands%2C%20but%20the%20people%20don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20realize%20it%2C%20they%20are%20still%20guilty.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_4_14%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20they%20become%20aware%20of%20their%20sin%2C%20the%20people%20must%20bring%20a%20young%20bull%20as%20an%20offering%20for%20their%20sin%20and%20present%20it%20before%20the%20Tabernacle.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_4_15%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20elders%20of%20the%20community%20must%20then%20lay%20their%20hands%20on%20the%20bull%26%23x2019%3Bs%20head%20and%20slaughter%20it%20before%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_4_16%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20high%20priest%20will%20then%20take%20some%20of%20the%20bull%26%23x2019%3Bs%20blood%20into%20the%20Tabernacle%2C%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_4_17%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3Edip%20his%20finger%20in%20the%20blood%2C%20and%20sprinkle%20it%20seven%20times%20before%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20in%20front%20of%20the%20inner%20curtain.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_4_18%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20will%20then%20put%20some%20of%20the%20blood%20on%20the%20horns%20of%20the%20altar%20for%20fragrant%20incense%20that%20stands%20in%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20presence%20inside%20the%20Tabernacle.%20He%20will%20pour%20out%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20blood%20at%20the%20base%20of%20the%20altar%20for%20burnt%20offerings%20at%20the%20entrance%20of%20the%20Tabernacle.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_4_19%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2219%