When%20he%20becomes%20aware%20of%20his%20sin%2C%20he%20must%20bring%20as%20his%20offering%20a%20male%20goat%20with%20no%20defects.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_4_24%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20must%20lay%20his%20hand%20on%20the%20goat%26%23x2019%3Bs%20head%20and%20slaughter%20it%20at%20the%20place%20where%20burnt%20offerings%20are%20slaughtered%20before%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20This%20is%20an%20offering%20for%20his%20sin.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_4_25%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E25%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20priest%20will%20dip%20his%20finger%20in%20the%20blood%20of%20the%20sin%20offering%20and%20put%20it%20on%20the%20horns%20of%20the%20altar%20for%20burnt%20offerings.%20He%20will%20pour%20out%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20blood%20at%20the%20base%20of%20the%20altar.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_4_26%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E26%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20he%20must%20burn%20all%20the%20goat%26%23x2019%3Bs%20fat%20on%20the%20altar%2C%20just%20as%20he%20does%20with%20the%20peace%20offering.%20Through%20this%20process%2C%20the%20priest%20will%20purify%20the%20leader%20from%20his%20sin%2C%20making%20him%20right%20with%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20and%20he%20will%20be%20forgiven.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_4_27%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%224%22%20vn%3D%2227%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E27%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BIf%20any%20of%20the%20common%20people%20sin%20by%20violating%20one%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20commands%2C%20but%20they%20don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20realize%20it%2C%20they%20are%20still%20gu